data.description: Home awaits in this downtown Puyallup 4 bedroom 2 bth charmer! This home has been upgraded with abundant open space and modern features including fully remodeled kitchen w/ granite countertops, incredible island, new cabinetry, new stainless steel appliances, and more! Bathrooms completely updated to include a mstr and gst bth on the main level, lux vinyl tile floors, and new carpet! 3 bdrms upstairs w/ 2 bonus rms perfect for your office, yoga, or art rm, the possibilities are endless! New roof, ext paint, and gutters. Fully fenced yard w/plenty of gardening space, grape vines, and a cherry tree! Detached garage/shop - your choice!  Near shopping, restaurants, across Meeker elem school - a perfect location! Add your personal touch!!
